       D. Usability Goals
       
       1. Effective to use (effectiveness)
       - The user is able to experience the three main transactions that an ATM is designed for. It is to Withdraw, Deposit and Check the balance of the account. 
       -it has provided the appropriate functions that make it possible to accomplish the three main task

       2. Efficient to use (efficiency)
       - You can withdraw, check your balance, and deposit with ease. Transactions are quick and straightforward and can be done in a short period of time, there are no erroneous information present in the machine that can cause errors 
       - Money is immediately released from the machine the moment the user confirms the transaction. The process of Withdrawing did not take long. 
 
       3. Safe to use (safety)
       - The ATM gives out a message regarding additional charges that would occur upon transaction (If your card was issued abroad, 200 pesos would be charged)
       -it provides signals or warning on every action to avoid undesired transactions and make sure that users does not commit errors

       4. Having good utility (utility)
       - Despite the fact that a user could Withdraw, Deposit and Check one’s balance, a user also is given the option to pay his/her utility bills through the ATM. 
       - It has access with the leading companies in banking (CITIBANK, Standard Chartered and HSBC)

       5. Easy to learn (learnability)
       -there are provided instructions for every page, it signals the user what to input on that particular field that will allow him/her to know easily what action to be performed
       -only simple process is needed, labels of buttons are simple and straightforward,
       -by just pressing the buttons with its given function, it is possible to accomplish task. No other complicated actions are needed.

       6. Easy to remember how to use (memorability)
       -Even though there are multiple services provided by the ATM machine, it is memorable because of the buttons accommodated with simple labels provided, it is only a simple process to operate the machine, by just clicking buttons with their given functions, the task could be accomplished. No other extra activities are required.

       
